{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3bf738d4-cc97-40c2-b0d6-7ba73daf32bd","content":"Here's the setup:\n\n**AppShell.xaml**\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<Shell\n    x:Class=\"MyApp.AppShell\"\n    xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n    xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n    xmlns:views=\"clr-namespace:MyApp.Views\"\n    FlyoutBehavior=\"Flyout\">\n\n    <!-- Dashboard: single page in its own section -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Dashboard\" Icon=\"dashboard.png\">\n        <ShellContent\n            Title=\"Dashboard\"\n            ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:DashboardPage}\"\n            Route=\"dashboard\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Products: two tabs (Active / Archived) -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Products\" Icon=\"products.png\">\n        <Tab Title=\"Products\">\n            <ShellContent\n                Title=\"Active\"\n                ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ActiveProductsPage}\"\n                Route=\"active\" />\n            <ShellContent\n                Title=\"Archived\"\n                ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ArchivedProductsPage}\"\n                Route=\"archived\" />\n        </Tab>\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Settings: separate flyout entry -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Settings\" Icon=\"settings.png\">\n        <ShellContent\n            Title=\"Settings\"\n            ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:SettingsPage}\"\n            Route=\"settings\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n</Shell>\n```\n\n**AppShell.xaml.cs**\n\n```csharp\nnamespace MyApp;\n\npublic partial class AppShell : Shell\n{\n    public AppShell()\n    {\n        InitializeComponent();\n\n        // Register route for detail page (not in visual hierarchy)\n        Routing.RegisterRoute(\"productdetails\", typeof(Views.ProductDetailsPage));\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Navigating to the detail page** (e.g., from ActiveProductsPage):\n\n```csharp\nawait Shell.Current.GoToAsync(\"productdetails\", new Dictionary<string, object>\n{\n    [\"Product\"] = selectedProduct\n});\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n| Concept | What it does |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `FlyoutItem` | Top-level flyout menu entry |\n| `Tab` with multiple `ShellContent` | Bottom tabs within one flyout item |\n| `Routing.RegisterRoute` | Enables navigation to pages not in the Shell visual tree |\n| `ContentTemplate` + `DataTemplate` | Lazy-loads pages on first visit |\n\nThe `Tab` wrapper around the two `ShellContent` items gives you the bottom tab bar for Active/Archived when \"Products\" is selected. The registered route lets you push `ProductDetailsPage` onto the navigation stack from either tab.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"84680137-f871-4168-bb1d-bc8af8f78730","outputTokens":697,"requestId":"A846:1F56EA:6DE1F5:7EEE3E:69FBE4A1"},"id":"fbb436df-3577-4ca1-bd92-1c8329858fee","timestamp":"2026-05-07T01:02:41.595Z","parentId":"8731cfb5-93d1-412f-a241-78bd89c04cef"}
